regex backtracking in IDEs
IDE	find	replace	find/replace shortcut
	PSpad	(group)	$1	ctrl+h
	Netbeans**	(group)	$1
	Jdev	(group)	\1	ctrl+r
	eclipse	(group)	\1	ctrl+f
	vim*	:% s/\(group\)/\1\1/g	% whole file, /g all occurences
	visual studio 	(group)\1	$1	you are really to capture in “find” with “\” and in “replace” with “$”
	IntelliJ	(group)	\$1


